These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: animation, zombie, action, disaster, western, epic
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, italian, turkish, chinese, canadian, polish
1. the argentine is the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is the polish##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
4. the argentine is between the polish and the canadian##2
5. the canadian is in an even position##4
6. the italian is on the far right##1
7. the italian is on the left or right of the turkish##3
8. the person watching epic movies is the turkish##1
9. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |     3      |  4   |     5      |    6    |
| Movie-Genre         | western     | action | animation | disaster | epic      | zombie |
| Nationality   | chinese | canadian  | argentine    | polish | turkish | italian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: daffodil, poppy, zinnia, aconite, daisy, lily
6 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, mouse, hedgehog, fish, chinchilla
 1. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 5. the person who growszinnia is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the owner of the fish is in an even position##4
 9. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
10. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |      5      |    6    |
| Flower   | daffodil  | aconite  | daisy | poppy   | lily | zinnia |
| Pet   | mouse | fish | lizard    | chinchilla | ferret   | hedgehog   |

