.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: fanta, water, mirinda, lemonade, cola, juice
There are 6 different favourite colors: apricot, amber, ebony, white, mauve, lavender
1. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
3. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
4. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
7. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person drinking water##1
8. the person who likes apricot is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person who likes white is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |    3    |       4       |     5      |    6     |
| Beverage   | fanta    | cola | mirinda     | water         | lemonade       | juice     |
| Color         | apricot | ebony  | amber | lavender | mauve | white |

