.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-4::.
6 different pets are kept: bird, mouse, dog, goat, turtle, hedgehog
6 different games are played: bridge, backgammon, domino, billiard, chess, go
1. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
3. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
4. the person playing billiard is in an even position##4
5. the person playing domino is the owner of the dog##1
6. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
7. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
8. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
9. the person playing go is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Pet   | bird | mouse     | dog     | goat | turtle | hedgehog |
| Game     | go    | backgammon | domino | billiard  | chess       | bridge      |

