.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-5::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: light-blue, turquise, grey, lavender, mauve, chestnut
The people have 6 different jobs:  manager, paramedic, software-developer, entrepreneur, coach, engineer
 1. the entrepreneur is between the person who likes grey and the software-developer##2
 2. the person who likes turquise is the engineer##1
 3. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the coach##1
 4. the coach is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 5. the engineer is on the right of the coach##1
 6. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 7. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
 8. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 9. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
10. the software-developer is on the left or right of the manager##3
11. the person who likes turquise is on the far right##1
12. the entrepreneur is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |     4      |     5      |    6    |
| Color   | mauve | lavender | light-blue | chestnut    | grey    | turquise |
| Job     | paramedic         | manager       | software-developer  | entrepreneur | coach | engineer   |

