.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-6::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: aquamarine, red, black, azure, yellow, green
6 different games are played: snooker, backgammon, canasta, billiard, go, scrabble
 1. the person playing backgammon is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 4. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 5. the person who likes black is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who likes red is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 8. the person who likes azure is the person playing billiard##1
 9. the person who likes black is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6    |
| Color   | black   | yellow   | azure    | green    | red  | aquamarine   |
| Game   | scrabble | canasta | billiard | snooker | go | backgammon |

