.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-7::.
6 different games are played: domino, whist, mah-jongg, chess, poker, go
House: cape-cod, futuristic, gothic-revival, wooden, art-deco, modern
 1. the modern house is the person playing go##1
 2. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
 3. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
 4. the futuristic house is on the far left##1
 5. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person playing go##1
 6. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 7. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the modern house##1
 9. the person playing domino is in an even position##4
10. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2       |         3          |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Game     | chess | whist     | poker | domino  | mah-jongg     | go |
| House   | futuristic         | art-deco | wooden              | gothic-revival | cape-cod | modern |

