There are 6 different nationalities: mexican, egyptian, dutch, colombian, pakistani, argentine
House: victorian, futuristic, modern, tower, cape-cod, cottage
 1. the futuristic house is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the tower house is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
 3. the futuristic house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 4. the modern house is on the left of the tower house##1
 5. the egyptian is on the left of the argentine##1
 6. the cape-cod house is on the right of the argentine##1
 7. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4
 8. the dutch is in an even position##4
 9. the dutch is on the right of the mexican##1
10. the victorian house is in an odd position##4
11. the colombian is on the far right##1
12. the cottage house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |    3     |       4       |     5      |      6       |
| Nationality   | mexican | dutch     | egyptian | argentine         | pakistani        | colombian       |
| House      | modern       | tower | victorian  | cottage | cape-cod | futuristic |

