3. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
4. the person who growstulip is in an even position##4
5. the owner of the cat is between the person who growsdaisy and the owner of the snake##2
6. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
7. the person who growstulip is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
8. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4       |   5    |     6     |
