.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-10::.
6 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, monopoly, scrabble, billiard, bridge
House: colonial, modern, ranch-style, cottage, townhouse, art-deco
 1. the cottage house is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing billiard##2
 2. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
 3. the art-deco house is on the left of the modern house##1
 4. the person playing bridge is the cottage house##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 6. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
 7. the ranch-style house is the person playing canasta##1
 8. the colonial house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
 9. the person playing backgammon is the townhouse house##1
10. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
11. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |       3       |   4   |     5     |    6    |
| Game    | backgammon | scrabble | monopoly | bridge | billiard      | canasta    |
| House   | townhouse       | art-deco      | modern     | cottage  | colonial | ranch-style |

