.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-11::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, lemonade, juice, coffee, milk
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: dubstep, jazz, rock, house, salsa, gospel
 1. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
