 3. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
 4. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 5. the person drinking juice is between the fan of jazz and the person drinking water##2
 6. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
 7. the fan of house is the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the person drinking milk is on the right of the fan of house##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
10. the person drinking milk is the fan of dubstep##1
11. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |       4       |     5      |    6    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | juice | water | lemonade       | milk    | coffee  |
| Music-Genre         | jazz     | rock   | gospel    | house | dubstep | salsa |

