.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-15::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, fanta, tea, water, 7up
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: adventure, romance, thriller, scientific, musical, comedy
 1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching romance movies##2
 5. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person watching romance movies is in an even position##4
 8. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 9. the person watching adventure movies is the person drinking lemonade##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Beverage        | tea | fanta | water | milk      | 7up | lemonade |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | thriller | comedy   | romance | scientific    | adventure |

