.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-16::.
City: paris, rome, san-francisco, boston, marseilles, berlin
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: rugby, biathlon, baseball, swimming, tennis, climbing
 1. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
 3. the person traveling to paris is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
 7. the person traveling to paris is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is the person traveling to rome##1
 9. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
10. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |       5       |     6     |
| City   | berlin | san-francisco    | rome | paris | boston | marseilles |
| Sport     | swimming      | baseball | climbing  | biathlon    | tennis        | rugby      |

