 6. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
 7. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the rabbit##1
 8. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
