.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3       |     4     |    5    |     6     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | spy   | fantasy      | musical | sports  | crime |
| Pet         | snake  | turtle | pony | ferret  | rabbit | hamster   |

