.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-20::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, cain, vegafina, swisher, pall-mall, game
6 different pets are kept: rat, turtle, hamster, snake, pony, hedgehog
 1. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
 2. the pall-mall-smoker is in an even position##4
 3. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 4. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 6. the chaman-smoker is the owner of the pony##1
 7. the vegafina-smoker is in an even position##4
 8. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the rat is between the pall-mall-smoker and the owner of the turtle##2
10. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
11. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
12. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |   3    |   4    |       5        |     6      |
| Cigar   | chaman    | vegafina      | swisher  | pall-mall  | game           | cain  |
| Pet    | pony | turtle | rat | snake | hedgehog | hamster |

 